;   Json_util, String_util -> masc_core   (wrapped false)
;   Masc_domain            -> masc_types  (wrapped false; iso8601/now helpers)
;   Yojson, Unix           -> external
; No flat-ns masc module appears below, so a future re-coupling becomes a dune
; cycle that audit-sublib-cycle.py / dune build rejects (RFC-0056 G1).

